    "AGENT-TO-AGENT (built, release-gated): Databricks MAS 'Pattern 4 Retention Supervisor' (mas-77bd204b-endpoint) + CE askRetentionAgent + a Domo AI Agent tile in the workflow are built/validated. TO GO LIVE: (1) coordinated pattern4ce release that includes askRetentionAgent; (2) bump CE_VERSION in scripts/create_pattern4_workflow.py to that release and re-run (re-PUTs the workflow definition); (3) Deploy workflow 1.0.0; (4) domo publish + re-instantiate the App Studio card (18 aliases).",
